"""seed curated hardware reference entries

Revision ID: 56b03c3c66b8
Revises: 51d02959d4c5
Create Date: 2026-07-20 10:24:02.826986

Bakes the curated Nintendo/Sony/Microsoft hardware dataset (normally loaded via
`python -m scripts.import_hardware_reference` from data/hardware/*.xlsx) directly into a
migration. The source spreadsheets aren't committed to this repo, so a fresh deploy (e.g. a
new Docker container) previously had no way to populate hardware_reference_entries at all,
leaving the Brand/Console/Variant cascade on Add Device/Add Accessory empty. `INSERT OR
IGNORE` keyed off the existing unique `official_name` index makes this safe to run against a
dev DB that already has this data from a manual import.
"""
